<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Contrat de commande — Poulets BF</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bf-green: #2E7D32;
      --bf-green-dark: #14532D;
      --bf-amber: #FF8F00;
      --ink: #0F172A;
      --ink-soft: #475569;
      --ink-muted: #94A3B8;
      --paper: #FFFFFF;
      --border-fine: #D1D5DB;
    }
    @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm; margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--paper);
      font-family: 'Noto Sans', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink); font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm;
      padding: 12mm 15mm;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding-bottom: 5mm;
      border-bottom: 2pt solid var(--bf-green);
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .brand strong {
      font-size: 18pt;
      color: var(--bf-green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .brand span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
    }
    .doc-meta {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
    }
    .doc-meta strong { color: var(--ink); font-size: 11pt; display: block; }

    h1 {
      font-size: 22pt;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 2mm;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 11pt;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }

    .parties {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 6mm;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .party {
      padding: 5mm;
      background: #F9FAFB;
      border-left: 3pt solid var(--bf-amber);
    }
    .party h3 {
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5pt;
      margin-bottom: 2mm;
    }
    .party strong { font-size: 13pt; display: block; color: var(--ink); }
    .party span { display: block; font-size: 9pt; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-top: 1mm; }

    .order-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 6mm;
    }
    .order-table th {
      background: var(--bf-green);
      color: #FFFFFF;
      padding: 3mm;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 9pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.3pt;
    }
    .order-table td {
      padding: 3mm;
      border-bottom: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
      font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .order-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .order-table .right { text-align: right; }
    .order-table .total-row {
      background: #E8F5E9;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-top: 2pt solid var(--bf-green);
    }
    .order-table .total-row td { color: var(--bf-green-dark); font-size: 12pt; }

    .terms {
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
      padding: 4mm;
      background: #FFF8E1;
      border-left: 3pt solid var(--bf-amber);
      font-size: 9pt;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .terms h4 {
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      margin-bottom: 2mm;
    }

    .signatures {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8mm;
      margin-top: 15mm;
    }
    .sig-block {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 15mm;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--ink);
    }
    .sig-block strong { display: block; font-size: 10pt; }
    .sig-block span { display: block; font-size: 9pt; color: var(--ink-soft); }

    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 8mm; left: 15mm; right: 15mm;
      font-size: 7pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
      padding-top: 3mm;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header class="header">
      <div class="brand">
        <strong>Poulets BF</strong>
        <span>FASO DIGITALISATION · Burkina Faso</span>
      </div>
      <div class="doc-meta">
        <strong>Contrat N° {{orderId}}</strong>
        Émis le {{dateCommande}}
      </div>
    </header>

    <h1>Contrat de commande</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Accord commercial client — éleveur</p>

    <section class="parties">
      <div class="party">
        <h3>Client</h3>
        <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>
        <span>{{clientAddress}}</span>
        <span>{{clientPhone}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="party">
        <h3>Éleveur</h3>
        <strong>{{eleveurName}}</strong>
        <span>{{eleveurRegion}}</span>
        <span>{{eleveurPhone}}</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <table class="order-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Désignation</th>
          <th class="right">Quantité</th>
          <th class="right">Prix unitaire</th>
          <th class="right">Total</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <strong>{{race}}</strong><br>
            <span style="color: var(--ink-muted); font-size: 9pt;">Lot {{lotId}} · Poids moyen {{poidsKg}} kg</span>
          </td>
          <td class="right">{{quantity}}</td>
          <td class="right">{{prixUnitaire}} FCFA</td>
          <td class="right">{{sousTotal}} FCFA</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="3" class="right">Frais de livraison</td>
          <td class="right">{{fraisLivraison}} FCFA</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="total-row">
          <td colspan="3" class="right">TOTAL TTC</td>
          <td class="right">{{amount}} FCFA</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <section class="terms">
      <h4>Modalités</h4>
      <ul style="padding-left: 5mm;">
        <li>Livraison prévue : <strong>{{dateLivraison}}</strong> à l'adresse client ci-dessus.</li>
        <li>Paiement : <strong>{{paiementMode}}</strong> — confirmé à la livraison ou avant selon entente.</li>
        <li>Certification halal : lot {{#if halalCertified}}<strong style="color:#2E7D32">CERTIFIÉ</strong>{{else}}non certifié{{/if}}.</li>
        <li>En cas de litige, les parties saisissent la plateforme de médiation Poulets BF.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="signatures">
      <div class="sig-block">
        <strong>Le Client</strong>
        <span>{{clientName}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sig-block">
        <strong>L'Éleveur</strong>
        <span>{{eleveurName}}</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      Document généré le {{issuedAt}} · Poulets BF · FASO DIGITALISATION<br>
      Ce document est exécutoire dès signature des deux parties.
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
